# CyberThreatGotchi — authorized lab targets (Hacker Planet LLC defensive lab ONLY)
# Copy to lab-targets.conf (gitignored) and edit IPs for your environment.
# Before nmap, metasploit, burp, or sqlmap: destination MUST appear in this file (uncommented).
#
# NOT ALLOWED: public internet sweeps, neighbors, coffee-shop WiFi, production SaaS without ROE.
# See docs/KALI_LAB_ARCHITECTURE.md § Lab anonymity & authorized pentest

# Localhost services inside Kali VM
127.0.0.1

# VirtualBox NAT default segment (adjust if your hypervisor differs)
10.0.2.0/24

# Documented lab VLAN (LAN_LAB) — example from KALI_LAB_ARCHITECTURE.md
192.168.50.0/24

# Placeholders — replace with your DVWA / Metasploitable VM IPs when VMs exist
